events.name: Anaheim Ducks at Detroit Red Wings

headlines.description: Adam Henrique scored his fourth goal in two games and the Anaheim Ducks held off the Detroit Red Wings 4-3 on Monday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Henrique scores 4th goal in 2 games as Ducks down slumping Red Wings, 4-3

headlines.description: Justin Barron scored a power-play goal 1:09 into overtime to lift the Montreal Canadiens to a 3-2 victory over the Winnipeg Jets on Monday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Barron scores in OT to lift Canadiens to 3-2 win over Jets

video.headline: Justin Barron buries overtime winner for Canadiens

headlines.description: Matt Duchene scored twice and assisted on Thomas Harleys goal 2:16 into overtime that gave the Dallas Stars a 4-3 victory over the Seattle Kraken on Monday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Duchene scores twice and sets up Harley's overtime goal to give Stars 4-3 win over Kraken

video.headline: Thomas Harley nets the game winner for Stars in overtime

tracking.trackingName: NHL_One-Play (Thomas Harley nets the game winner for Stars in overtime) 2023/12/19 ESHEET

headlines.description: Mikael Backlund scored a tiebreaking short-handed goal early in the third period, Jacob Markstrom stopped 34 shots, and the Calgary Flames beat the Florida Panthers 3-1 on Monday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Backlund scores short-handed goal in 3rd period as Flames beat Panthers 3-1

video.headline: Mikael Backlund scores shorty vs. Panthers
